    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been super reliable and drives like a dream. I\u2019m sad to part with it, but I know it\u2019s going to make the next owner so happy. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
