    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features the original, deep-gloss factory paint with zero swirls, chips, or imperfections, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment since new. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, showing no signs of weather exposure or corrosion. From the crisp response of the engine to the factory-fresh feel of the suspension, this is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. No modifications, no stories\u2014just pure, original excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
