      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in concours-level condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly superlative motorcar.",
