      "description": "This 997.2-generation Carrera S represents the zenith of naturally aspirated performance and mechanical purity. At its heart lies a 3.8L flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), providing immediate throttle response and a broad torque curve. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power distribution. This example features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for superior lateral stability and high-frequency damping control. Maintained to a concours standard, the vehicle shows zero signs of thermal stress or mechanical fatigue, with a pristine undercarriage and factory-spec paint depth. It is a mechanically synchronized masterpiece, offering a visceral, analog driving experience in showroom condition.",
